<Defs>
	<!-- ||| Leo Skin Main Gene ||| -->
	<GeneDef>
		<defName>JAR_LeoSkin</defName>
		<label>leoskin</label>
		<labelShortAdj>pantherinaeSkinned</labelShortAdj>
		<description>The carriers of this gene grow a uniform, thin layer of fur across their body. Despite its appearances and ease of cleaning, fur is still fur, helping guard against the cold of winter, designed to be comfortable while huddled against other carriers of this gene, the carrier doesnâ€™t overheat as easily as other coats.</description>
		<biostatCpx>0</biostatCpx>
		<biostatMet>0</biostatMet>
		<displayCategory>Miscellaneous</displayCategory>
		<displayOrderInCategory>400</displayOrderInCategory>
		<iconPath>UI/GeneIcons/Gene_LeoSkin</iconPath>
		<iconColor>(0.75, 0.75, 0.75)</iconColor>
		<forcedHeadTypes>
			<li>JAR_LeoSkin_Narrow</li>
			<li>JAR_LeoSkin_Average</li>
			<li>JAR_LeoSkin_Wide</li>
			<li>JAR_LeoSkin_Gaunt</li>
		</forcedHeadTypes>
		<hairTagFilter>
		<whitelist>true</whitelist>
			<tags>
				<li>JAR_LeoBeard</li>
			</tags>
		</hairTagFilter>
		<exclusionTags>
			<li>Hair</li>
			<li>Fur</li>
		</exclusionTags>
		<statOffsets>
			<ComfyTemperatureMin>-5</ComfyTemperatureMin>
		</statOffsets>
		<missingGeneRomanceChanceFactor>0.03</missingGeneRomanceChanceFactor>
		<graphicData>
			<fur>JAR_LeoSkin</fur>
			<colorType>Hair</colorType>
			<skinIsHairColor>true</skinIsHairColor>
			<tattoosVisible>true</tattoosVisible>
		</graphicData>
	</GeneDef>
	
	<!-- ||| Tigris Skin Main Gene ||| -->
	<GeneDef>
		<defName>JAR_TigrisSkin</defName>
		<label>Tigriskin</label>
		<labelShortAdj>pantherinaeSkinned</labelShortAdj>
		<description>The carriers of this gene grow a stripped, thick layer of fur across their body. The heaviness of this coat is an excellent defense of cold of any kind, even carrying smoother strands that allow for water to pass off strands easier than other hairs. Its pattern is a passive intimidation against simple creatures, informing any who look at the carrier of the threat.</description>
